    <!-- FAQ -->
    <string name="faq">FAQ</string>
    <string name="still_have_problems_1">Still have problems</string>
    <string name="cannot_connect_to_wifi_faq"><![CDATA[Can\'t connect to Wi-Fi?#\n1. Make sure you are <b>within the Wi-Fi coverage area</b>, and the Wi-Fi username and password are correct.\n\nIf you still can’t connect, please ask the QR code provider whether the password has been changed.\n\n2. If the scan result is displayed as text, you need to <b>manually connect to Wi-Fi</b> in your phone\'s network settings based on the Wi-Fi name and password provided in the text.]]></string>
    <string name="code_cannot_be_read_faq"><![CDATA[Code can\'t be read?#\n1. In order to get accurate scanning results, please make sure that the code meets the following characteristics:\n\t\ta. rich contrast and <b>not blurry</b>.\n\t\tb. <b>no light reflections or shadows</b> on the code.\n\t\tc. <b>complete</b>, with no missing parts.\n\n2. If you are using a low-end phone, scanning may be very difficult or even impossible due to the low camera quality.\n\nYou could try to take a photo with your camera app, then open our app and tap \'Scan from the gallery\' to solve this problem.\n\n3. If you still can\'t get the result when scanning the barcode or QR code, please send an email via %sfeedback%s to us, we will solve the problem for you as soon as possible.]]></string>
    <string name="convert_picture_to_qr_code_faq"><![CDATA[Convert a picture to a QR code?#\nThe function will be launched soon…]]></string>
    <string name="have_problem_with_the_link_faq"><![CDATA[Have problem with the link you get?#\n1. This app can\'t change the content of the QR code, so if you can\'t open this website, it is more likely that there is a problem with the <b>website itself</b>. Unfortunately, there is nothing we can do about it.\n\n2. It is also possible that the creator of the QR code entered the <b>wrong link</b> or the QR code has <b>expired</b>, causing you to be unable to open the website. If possible, you can try to confirm the correctness of the QR code with the creator.\n\n3. In particular, some web links need to be opened under special conditions, for example, they need to be opened using a <b>certain app</b>. Please follow the instructions of the QR code provider.]]></string>
    <string name="need_more_information_faq"><![CDATA[Need more information?#\nThere is too much information and we may not be able to provide the information you want every time. You can check for more information through <b>Web Search</b>.\n\nIf Web Search still can\'t help you find the information you are looking for, it may be that the code itself contains limited information. Please understand.]]></string>
